+### Step 3: Send a request (in another terminal)
+
+```bash
+curl -s http://localhost:3000/hello
+```
+
+**Terminal 1 output (where mkctl is running):**
+```
+[http] [2025-10-17T04:15:23.456Z] GET /hello
+```
+
+**Terminal 2 output (where curl ran):**
